---
import LegalLayout from '../layouts/LegalLayout.astro';
import { companyStats } from '../data/company-stats';
const { entity } = companyStats.legal;
---

<LegalLayout
  title="Cookie Policy"
  description="How Pacific Ocean Tech uses cookies and similar technologies."
  slug="cookie-policy"
>
  <h1>Cookie Policy</h1>
  <p>This Cookie Policy explains how {entity} (trading as "Pacific Ocean Tech") uses cookies and similar technologies on our website.</p>

  <h2>What are cookies?</h2>
  <p>Cookies are small text files stored on your device when you visit a website. They help sites function, remember preferences, and understand usage.</p>

  <h2>Types we use</h2>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Strictly necessary:</strong> Required for security, load balancing, and basic navigation.</li>
    <li><strong>Functional:</strong> Remember theme preferences (e.g., light/dark mode) and form progress.</li>
    <li><strong>Analytics:</strong> Help us understand traffic and improve content (e.g., page views, referrers). We aim to use privacy-respecting analytics where possible.</li>
    <li><strong>Marketing (if enabled):</strong> Measure campaign performance and retargeting, only with consent where required.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Third-party cookies</h2>
  <p>Embedded tools such as Calendly scheduling and the Tawk.to live-chat widget may set their own cookies governed by those providers' policies. These are treated as non-essential and are loaded only after you accept them via our cookie banner (or where consent is not legally required).</p>

  <h2>Your choices</h2>
  <p>When you first visit our site, a cookie banner lets you accept all cookies or limit us to strictly necessary cookies only. Non-essential cookies (functional, analytics, and marketing) do not load until you consent. You can change your choice at any time by selecting "Cookie settings" in the banner footer, and you can also control cookies through your browser settings—blocking cookies may affect site functionality.</p>

  <h2>Updates</h2>
  <p>We may revise this policy as our site evolves. Check this page for the latest version.</p>

  <h2>Contact</h2>
  <p>{entity}<br />Email: privacy@pacificoceantech.com</p>
</LegalLayout>
